🐝 Busy Bee

> Stop being just a busy bee; start getting things done.


Busy Bee is a task-management web application designed to help users track high-level goals by breaking them into manageable, time-sensitive "Mini Tasks." Built with Django, HTMX, and Tailwind CSS, it focuses on speed and "quick wins" to maintain productivity momentum.

✨ Key Features
🎯 Goal Decomposition: Break large tasks into smaller "Mini Tasks" to reduce overwhelm.
⏱️ Precise Deadlines: Real-time validation prevents past-dated tasks and tracks exact minute-by-minute completion.
⚡ Reactive UI: Powered by HTMX for a smooth, single-page experience without full page reloads.
📊 Productivity Insights: Track your "was on time" percentage and view detailed completion logs.
🎨 Dynamic Styling: Modern, responsive UI built with DaisyUI and Tailwind CSS.

🛠️ Tech Stack
``` Backend: Django 5.0+ (Python)
Frontend: HTMX (for AJAX-driven interactions), Tailwind CSS & DaisyUI
Database: PostgreSQL (Production), SQLite (Local development)
Deployment: Render
Environment: Pipenv (Virtual environment and dependency management) ```